</li>
<li class="image-gallery-item">
<div><a href="../../../gerandocidadania/galeria/conferencia-dca-sisal/concriancasisal1.jpg?view=true"><img src="../../../thumbnails/0004/1081/concriancasisal1_thumb.JPG?1251396654" alt="Concriancasisal1_thumb"></a></div>
</li>
<li class="image-gallery-item">
